content.rendered:
This service includes a 10-hour engagement with our technical & SEO experts.

We will audit your site and determine points of improvement for on-site SEO, run an analysis of backlinks, a link profile comparison with your competitors, and develop a strategy to improve your site’s rankings.

excerpt.rendered: 10-hour engagement with our technical & SEO experts. This SEO audit will identify areas of improvement for your site & map out a course of action to improve your rankings.
